      <odd id="aspace_d06d3b8e2eb46585a0dd7a1abf4601c8">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 46-A (YRG 46-A), Records and materials broadly documenting Yale buildings, facilities, and grounds.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_edc98d2847f095702d1c80135fbdc928">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The materials were donated by Dr. Henry Hunn, Sheffield Scientific School, Class of 1914.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
